node.text: I wish I could repay you for EVERYTHING you have done for my sister and I but there’s no way I could….You have been there for me since the second I was born with so much unconditional love…Your love is pure and it is limitless. I would NOT be where I am today nor be the woman I am today without you mom. You have loved me at my worst, you have loved me at my best, you loved me even when I didn’t love myself and you loved me even when I didn’t always do the right thing. THANK YOU for never giving up on me and always believing in me even when I didn’t believe in myself. HAPPY BIRTHDAY MOM!💓😍❤️💖(there’s so much more to come for your birthday weekend soon!) TE AMO!💜
